6. Source of funds: We run a poker players community, share a part of the revenue coming from our player’s rake and keep some to ourselves as a profit. 

Why need funds? I am Ukrainian, rn my family is stuck in Kyiv as well as many friends. I have supported Ukrainian humanitarian needs (food, diapers, medications) since the war started. Proof of a transfer from my eth wallet to “Unchain Ukraine” charity fund: https://etherscan.io/tx/0x7ef9123eeb7d5acffee57fba2da844b70a1f4194a45768eab3a99a80114b3652

Link: https://unchain.fund/ (funds are being raised by NEAR blockchain, they are legit). 

Around 40k sent for affected people through CEX account to friends, just random guys, and families from my facebook network. 

Willing to keep donating from the hacked funds if you decide to recover. Able to KYC, provide additional proofs, share my social profiles if required.
